Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這麼多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只要過了這關 就有大量的同人志在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上次去的秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及社團教室裏的同人志推測
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有值得期待的好作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原 你是第一次參加同人志販售會對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.76,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京國際展覽中心舉辦的 Comic Market，OTAKU的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來好像很累 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從昨天開始就一直興奮到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會累成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就說累還太早喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阪跟其他人的感覺完全不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的OTAKU比率…難道是100%？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:52.30,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（國際展覽館站）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨將至的預感啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是斑目用來塑造自己角色個性的一環啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽聽就好 什麼都不要回他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,266)}地域文化振興的問題點及其功績
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是搭第一班電車來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼隊伍已經排到這麼遠了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎 大概是熬夜來排隊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說禁止熬夜排隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說天氣這麼糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是狂風暴雨 就越要來排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還沒瘋狂到那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要是春日部在場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又會狠狠的吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我想她應該不會明白這其中的深刻涵義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股熱氣是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都那麼有精神呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為天氣不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有會發生什麼事件的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候一定很適合進行宗教體驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管什麼宗教體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種天氣確實挺罕見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近比較少聽人提到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 以前大家都說「夏季 Comic Festival」時一定不會下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那種說法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得 今天一定會發生什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同神跡般的大事件！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完全搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走走停停的 煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過確實有在前進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完全陷入了「跑步者的愉悅感」的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳跺來跺去的 很煩人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去跑個幾圈再回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會幫你佔著位子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要去跑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的 騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會做出擾亂隊伍的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑目 你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟臉的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事有可能會成為傳說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 骨折了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 手指頭還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有斷掉才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在買同人志前 要先到公司的攤位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以拿到「巷談社」發行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不平衡抽籤」動畫化紀念限定收集卡為優先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是只要排隊就能拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很輕鬆的就能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要排隊就能拿到的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他安靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總是會不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就撐到不能撐為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往神的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺能直達天堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\an8}目前場內參觀人數眾多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\an8}請各位不要著急 慢慢移動您的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\an8}並感謝您的合作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海報 墊板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要不要先確認一下收集卡的內容呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在那之前 先去排專門領取收集卡的隊伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有重複的話 到時候不要排就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑目？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…今天限定的稀有卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我來分類一下 大家的先交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？斑目的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原 你幫我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤的時候 我好像扭到手腕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？有沒有腫起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼看都像是扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至比扭到更嚴重…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我都忘了要模仿鐵雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.27,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵雄：出自大友克洋的 AKIRA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是直接到醫院去比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「福要緊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都那麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了…稀有卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到神了…的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別再耍寶了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難受 不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的不要緊嗎？斑目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸的感覺不到痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那很糟耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話 接下來才是重頭戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來到東館了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你手變成那樣 沒辦法買東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要貼在屜原背上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正身高也剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也喜歡就叫他買兩本 錢回去再算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 照你的興趣去選就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不要這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原 你好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘地下鐵的第一班電車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排了老長的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍受了五個小時的悶熱暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服了我的傷勢 以及限定商品的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在寶藏山就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的話 你會在這裏臨陣脫逃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該沒有克服傷勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼 早就麻痹了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作沒看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說真的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:09:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太誇張了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真的昏倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜…屜原 快…快去叫工作人員過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是敗給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是大腦刻意中斷了他的意識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像跳電一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他一直在死撐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪…陪他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我陪他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還醒著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著陪我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去買同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到讚的就買兩本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢…之後…再付…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會咬到舌頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常看到有人躺在擔架上被抬走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這種情況會發生在自己人的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我們就分頭去買自己想要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就約在這裏集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活著回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別學斑目的口氣說話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛才就聽斑目提過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都先確認過內容才買
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來真的可以這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這樣當然是再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有許多東西 我都不敢在同人店內翻閱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 就算買到不好的 我也不會怨人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在心中嘀咕個不停的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個請給我一本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,700元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\an8}不好意思 借過借過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「不簽」裏的會長的畫冊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且畫風我還蠻喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都沒有其他客人在看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幹嘛不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經在同人志販賣店裏鍛煉過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正在這裏的所有人都是——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…我可以看看內容嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本…不 請給我兩本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共是1000元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 列祖列宗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我沒去掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是跑來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說出了車站就動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算直接回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春日部她也很拼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩讓我拍幾張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請看一下這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 可以請你擺出十指交叉的姿勢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要拍了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 老是麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以收下嗎？梟先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是買太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完全融入其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要買這本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們已經完全是同類了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 竟然帶女朋友一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你怎麼展現出真實的自我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然裝模作樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿的衣服根本就不適合這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要買
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要買
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也要買
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是會長的畫冊 都無條件買下！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…有什麼開關就要被打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我頭頂附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原口？你怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還兼漫研社的社員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這裏是漫研的攤位嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有製作同人志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要買 我要買
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本送你 是新刊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我用買的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你 送你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然其他社員都沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你進來一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那邊的缺口進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是熱啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我坐下 害另一個人不得不站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家都面朝另一邊 完全無視我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的可以嗎？原口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？有買到好的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這次放棄買那些很熱門的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去排公司的攤位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 一開始就算想搶熱門的 也是很困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是一般參觀者 而且還得排隊進場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想買的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須成為參展者 從一開始就待在場內才有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現視研可能辦不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現視研目前有在進行什麼活動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實所謂的現視研
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是10年前左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越漫畫、動畫、電玩而成立的綜合性社團
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣反而造成社團活動內容的模糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果現在與每個社團都有重疊的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就結論而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現視研並沒有存在的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以裏面淨是些半調子的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強算是會動筆作畫的 只有久我山一個而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他只是塗鴉 並不製作成原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑目說起話來 雖然一副軍事OTAKU的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是在學吉翁軍而已 根本沒半點知識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於田中則是Cosplay…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那個叫什麼來著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從興趣看 似乎完全是個OTAKU
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是外表、行為、個性卻完全沒有OTAKU的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個怪傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 每年的現視研都聚集了一群不上不下的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己從沒創作出任何東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如趁現在退出 加入漫研吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 可是原口你不是兩邊都有參加嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是掛名而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有剛開始時去過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉得實際情況後就再沒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一年級的時候 會長他就是會長了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在到底是幾年級呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那樣反而比較適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些話都是我們私下聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別跟別人提喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你送我的新刊裏 有你畫的作品嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作就像編輯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門負責批評之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫研的同學 真是對不起你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前大家只要一談到原口 就會露出不愉快的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他是那種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}在此宣佈 「夏季 Comic Festival」第66屆的會期到此已全部結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…你逛蠻久的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在讓人眼花繚亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你有幫斑目買嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有幫他挑了幾本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是斑目私底下挺中意的社團的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:22:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我本來以為屜原跟斑目的喜好完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話似乎很難讓我高興起來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我買了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫得也蠻好看的 夠…夠H
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？屜原
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次參加 Comic Festival 的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就跟高阪之前說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現視研可能真的很適合我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好累喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天發生了那麼多事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過 可還沒完喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候也得排隊 囧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.66,0:24:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（斑目晴信）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（手部韌帶受傷掌骨骨折）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.33,0:24:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（近端指節間接扭傷）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（需兩個月才能痊癒）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.51,0:24:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原 第一次來茶水嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.08,0:24:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常我都是只到秋葉原 然後直接回去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日大 （日本大學）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.99,0:24:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明治 （明治大學）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.85,0:24:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊則是醫科齒科 （東京醫科齒科大學）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.39,0:24:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順天堂 （順天堂大學）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:24:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是名學區
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.59,0:24:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駿台 （同名補習班）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.86,0:25:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典·法蘭斯 （同名外語學校）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.13,0:25:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.13,0:25:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美學校 （同名藝術職業學校）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.00,0:25:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東設 （東京設計學院）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.43,0:25:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏面唯一不一樣的是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,266)}由偽裝與扮裝的異化而造成的心理隔閡昇華作用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:42.30,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝起きて　例によって　携帯忘れて　乗り遅れた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:48.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鈍行の窓に映る人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:52.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}日本中で誰にも負けない一つがあるにはあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:58.08,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an7}悲しいかな　人知れず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.66,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけども速くは走れない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんなに丈夫にできてない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:11.17,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an7}いざ行け　不屈のマイペース
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:17.61,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日の悲しみよ過ぎ去ってゆけ天気雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:20.24,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}二の足　二の舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.94,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一夜一夜に夢見頃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:28.28,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さらば悲しみよ大気圏の外へ出ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:33.85,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}上空めがけて大きな声を張り上げろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}このテンポで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今　このテンポで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:42.30,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}早上起床依舊忘了手機　趕不上電車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:48.18,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}映照在慢車窗戶上的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:52.98,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然也有不輸人的日本第一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:58.08,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an3}但很悲哀無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.66,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然跑得不快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.20,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}長得也不太強壯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:11.17,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an3}向前衝吧　不認輸的我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:17.61,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天的悲傷啊　快快過去吧　太陽雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:20.24,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躊躇不前　重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.94,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每晚每晚好作夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:28.28,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再會了哀傷　滾到大氣層外頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:33.85,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著天空大聲吶喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.12,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用這個節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.50,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在用這個節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:23:03.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}遠回りも近道もしないで僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:13.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}明日がくることを　怖がる事もなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:21.79,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}歩き続けた　深夜の井の頭通り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:32.43,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}鮮やかな夢だけ　長く影に延びた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:41.74,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}大人未満の僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:54.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}単純で難解な煌めくびいだま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:58.82,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}そこから覗いていた時間が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:03.53,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}たいしたものはなくたって　輝いてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:08.06,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}今　この手の中にあるびいだまから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:13.91,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}見えるものは　少し違うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:22.82,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}僕らのそばで　小さく光ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:23:03.50,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}我們不抄近路　也不走遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:13.58,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}也不畏懼明天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:21.79,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}持續走在深夜的井之頭大道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:32.43,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}只有繽紛的夢想　延伸出長長的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:41.74,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}尚未長大成人的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:54.28,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}是既單純又難解的耀眼彈珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:58.82,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}從那裏窺探到的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:03.53,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}即使並不稀奇　卻也閃閃發光
